gious animosities? What business practices might encourage an atmosphere in which constructive dialogue among spiritual traditions could proceed? The author concludes that by implementing the peaceful practices advocated by religions at their best, businesses can both nurture religious harmony and strengthen their communities.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBusiness ethics. 0aBusinessxReligious aspects. 0aPeace. 0aReligious ethics. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Government & Business.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030011467640uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030014954840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300149548423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300149548/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY